Modules:

main.py: load all required resources, manage savegames, hold needed pyglet utilities, menu system

classes.py: game entity classes, game event classes. Non-scene-specific.

library.py: game helper utilities, all functions

scene_name: scene with name, starting with tutorial.

Structure:

./	|	modules, readme, icons, etc.
./res	|	everything else: pictures, music, savegame, etc.
